          <span class="help-text"><span style="color:#800000">merge
          priority</span> specifies the CPU scheduler priority 
          at which merges should run.
          The settings are: </span>
	  <ul>
	   <li><span class="help-text">
           <span style="color:#800000">normal</span> 
           specifies the same CPU scheduler priority as for requests.
           </span></li>
	   <li><span class="help-text">
           <span style="color:#800000">lower</span> 
