	    <li><span class="help-text">Use the 
            <span style="color:#800000">Excludes</span> tab to add
	    excluded elements to the field you are currently
	    configuring. These elements can be reviewed and deleted on
	    the Configure page.</span></li>
            <li><span class="help-text">Use the 
            <span style="color:#800000">Create</span> 
            tab to create a new field.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <span class="help-text"></span>
         </admin:help>
         <admin:help xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
          <hr class="control-line" size="1"/>
          <span class="help-text"><p>Buttons and Tabs:</p></span>
          <ul>
	    <li><span class="help-text">Use the 
            <span style="color:#800000">Summary</span> tab to get a high
	    level view of the fields configured in this database.
	    Click on a field name to go to the detailed configuration
	    for that field.</span></li>
	    <li><span class="help-text">Use the 
            <span style="color:#800000">Configure</span> tab to get a high
	    level view of the fields configured in this
