            <span style="color:#800000">Excludes</span> tab to add
	    excluded elements to the field you are currently
	    configuring. These elements can be reviewed and deleted on
	    the Configure page.</span></li>
          </ul>
          <span class="help-text"></span>
         </admin:help>
      </xs:appinfo>
    </xs:annotation>
  </xs:element>

  <xs:complexType name="included-elements">
